Hack name - Clone Club

Functionality:
The user will enter his interests (like Movies, books and information about Flickr profile. He has to then submit this information to find his clone. This can be done in 3 modes:
1. User enters all the criterias to find the clone
2. User gives weightage to different criterias
3. User enters a single criteria

Based on the above 3 modes, the application will search for clones. It will then return a clone alongwith match percentage. 

Programming:
Probably use Yahoo! API's like Yahoo Location, Yahoo Movies and Yahoo local. 

Algorithm/Math functions:
We need to come up with a math function to take care of the weightage factor. 
